invoker.name: jira insight
invoker.description: Insight Asset Management is a Jira app. With the Insight feature in Jira Service Management, teams can track their assets, configuration items, and resources to understand and visualise the critical relationships between applications, services, their underlying infrastructure, and other key dependencies.
invoker.hint: This connector supports the Jira Datacenter or Server installation. It provides the basic auth. Check out the documentation https://confluence.atlassian.com/insightapps/insight-rest-api-1085180885.html
